information: The company ANTON GUGG GLOCKEN- UND KUNSTGIESSEREI GMBH, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1549, which operates in the Steel industry. It also operates in the Iron, special grade and pig iron, Copper and copper alloys, Public works contractors, and Well construction industries. It is based in Straubing, Germany.
